=Description=

"Creative Barcode is a new IPR – that enables companies, innovators &
creative individuals to authenticate, protect & safely disclose their
innovation concepts to potential partners/industry at concept &
pre-commercialisation phase. It is under-pinned by a Trust Charter and
safe-disclosure mechanism and endorsed by the World Intellectual Property
Organisation (WIPO)."



